'''軋空'''（{{lang-en|short squeeze}}），又稱'''逼空'''、'''空頭擠壓'''，是[[股市|股市]]術語之一，主要因市場供求關係，而非公司基本面變化而發生。當[[做空|做空]]者被迫平倉（清空[[部位_(期貨)|頭寸]]）而不斷買入標的股票時，市場上出現股票的需求量遠超過市面流通量情況，因供應不足而導致價格陡升現象發生時，可能出現軋空<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.investopedia.com/terms/s/shortsqueeze.asp |title=Short Squeeze |access-date=2010-09-17 |archive-date=2010-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100918073724/http://www.investopedia.com/terms/s/shortsqueeze.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==具體解釋==
[[短倉|做空]]是一種金融交易手法，其具體策略是做空者借入股票後立即將其出售，希望有投資者以低價買入這些股票。做空者最後必須將這些股票歸還給借貸方（且需要加上利息）。因此若多方買入股票的價格低於空方賣出股票的價格，空方即可獲利。然而預測股票價格非常困難，意外利好亦可能使得股票上漲，導致做空者出現虧損。在這種情況發生時，空方可能以比借入時更高的價格買入其借貸的股票，以防止出現股價進一步上漲使其虧損增加的情況。當空方購入股票以彌補頭寸，購買量大於市場供給量時，就出現了軋空。購買股票補倉的操作會增加被做空的股票的市值，從而引發更多做空者買入股票補倉，這種循環可能導致股價更大的上漲<ref name="WSJ 151205">{{Cite news |last=Constable |first=Simon |date=2015-12-06 |title=What Is a Short Squeeze? |work=Wall Street Journal |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/what-is-a-short-squeeze-1449460381 |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123063932/https://www.wsj.com/articles/what-is-a-short-squeeze-1449460381 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="FT 210125">{{Cite news |last=Powell |first=Jamie |date=2021-01-25 |title=GameStop can’t stop going up |work=FT Alphaville |url=https://www.ft.com/content/7aa60aa1-484f-4747-9136-cd0a560dd2d8 |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126233657/https://www.ft.com/content/7aa60aa1-484f-4747-9136-cd0a560dd2d8 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VoxGameStopExplosion">{{Cite web |last=Stewart |first=Emily |date=2021-01-28 |title=The GameStop stock frenzy, explained |url=https://www.vox.com/the-goods/22249458/gamestop-stock-wallstreetbets-reddit-citron/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128002059/https://www.vox.com/the-goods/22249458/gamestop-stock-wallstreetbets-reddit-citron |archive-date=2021-01-28 |access-date=2021-01-28 |website=[[Vox_(website)|Vox]] |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。借入、購買和售出股票的時機可能導致總股本以上的股份數被做空<ref>{{Cite web |last=Caplinger |first=Dan |date=2021-02-01 |title=Yes, a Stock Can Have Short Interest Over 100 Percent |url=https://www.fool.com/investing/2021/01/28/yes-a-stock-can-have-short-interest-over-100-heres/ |access-date=2021-02-01 |website=The motley fool |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129025346/https://www.fool.com/investing/2021/01/28/yes-a-stock-can-have-short-interest-over-100-heres/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Lewis SizemoreCaplinger |first=Charles |date=2021-02-01 |title=What Exactly Is a Short Squeeze? |url=https://www.kiplinger.com/investing/602165/what-exactly-is-a-short-squeeze |access-date=2021-02-01 |website=Kiplinger |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129180110/https://www.kiplinger.com/investing/602165/what-exactly-is-a-short-squeeze |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這種情況下，投機行為被稱為{{link-en|裸做空|naked short selling}}（naked short selling）。做空率過高的股票容易出現軋空的情況。高昂的借貸利率可能會增加做空者補倉的壓力，從而進一步加劇軋空現象。且股價井噴可能進一步導致追加保證金的情況，進而更加拉高股價，對空方形成惡性循環。

軋空較易發生在小盤股或成交不活躍的股票上。但股票流通量不足，且大多數持股者惜售時，也可能有軋空情況出現<ref>{{cite web |title=Short Squeezes |url=https://www.investorsunderground.com/short-squeezes/ |website=Investors Underground |accessdate=2016-11-11 |archive-date=2018-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180808043423/https://www.investorsunderground.com/short-squeezes/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

軋空的相反情況是{{link-en|軋多|long squeeze}}（{{lang|en|long squeeze}}），比軋空更少出現。在[[期貨|期貨]]市場上亦有軋空現象發生<ref>{{cite news |url=https://oilprice.com/Metals/Commodities/A-Short-Squeeze-In-Corn-May-Hit-The-Market.html |title=A Short Squeeze In Corn May Hit The Market |first=John |last=Thomas |date=2010-09-13 |journal=OilPrice.com |access-date=2021-01-25 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927073752/https://oilprice.com/Metals/Commodities/A-Short-Squeeze-In-Corn-May-Hit-The-Market.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==案例==
2008年10月，由於[[保時捷|保時捷]]試圖收購[[大众汽车|大众汽车]]，導致大众汽车股票出現短暫軋空現象，其在[[德國DAX指數|德國DAX指數]]上的股價在不足兩天的時間內從210.85歐元飆升至超過1,000歐元，一度成為世界市值最昂貴的公司<ref>{{Cite news |last=Gow |first=David |date=29 October 2009 |title=Porsche makes more VW stock available to desperate short-sellers |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2008/oct/29/vw-volkswagen-short-selling |access-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104091735/https://www.theguardian.com/business/2008/oct/29/vw-volkswagen-short-selling |archive-date=2021-01-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Krstić |first=Ivan |date=2009-01-07 |title=How Porsche hacked the financial system and made a killing |url=http://radian.org/notebook/porsche |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100815093759/http://radian.org/notebook/porsche |archive-date=2010-08-15 |access-date=2010-11-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。保時捷CEO{{link-en|溫德林·維德金|Wendelin Wiedeking}}因在事件中角色而被指控{{link-en|操縱市場|market manipulatio}}<ref>{{Cite web |date=2016-07-28 |title=Freispruch für Wiedeking rechtskräftig |url=http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/unternehmen/wendelin-wiedeking-freispruch-fuer-ex-porsche-chef-rechtskraeftig-a-1105143.html |access-date=2017-10-25 |website=[[Spiegel_Online|Spiegel Online]] |archive-date=2017-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313051602/http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/unternehmen/wendelin-wiedeking-freispruch-fuer-ex-porsche-chef-rechtskraeftig-a-1105143.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年，[[美國證券交易委員會|美國證券交易委員會]]指控{{link-en|菲利普·法爾科內|Philip Falcone}}對MAAX控股發行的一系列高利率債券進行軋空。在得知有公司做空債券後，法爾科內購買了全部債券，並將債券借給做空者，且在交易員售出時買回。這使得法爾科內持有的債券數超過了MAAX發行的債券總數。此後法爾科內停止借出債券，使空方無法清算頭寸，引發債券價格暴漲<ref name="NYT 120628">{{Cite news |last=Henning |first=Peter J. |date=2012-06-28 |title=In Case Against Philip Falcone, a Warning to Others |work=New York Times |url=https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2012/06/28/in-case-against-philip-falcone-a-warning-to-others/ |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2019-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002162857/https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2012/06/28/in-case-against-philip-falcone-a-warning-to-others/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MS 210126">{{Cite news |last=Levine |first=Matt |date=2021-01-26 |title=GameStop Is Just a Game |work=Bloomberg Opinion |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2021-01-26/will-wallstreetbets-face-sec-scrutiny-after-gamestop-rally |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129113728/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2021-01-26/will-wallstreetbets-face-sec-scrutiny-after-gamestop-rally |dead-url=no }}</ref>。空方被迫直接聯繫法爾科內，以進行平倉<ref name="MS 210126" />。

2015年11月，{{link-en|馬丁·什克雷里|Martin Shkreli}}對經營困難的生物技術公司KaloBios（KBIO）發動軋空，導致該公司股價在五個交易日內井噴10,000%。做空者曾認為KBIO公司「毫無疑問即將破產」<ref>{{Cite web |date=2018-08-01 |title=How Martin Shkreli caused a 10,000% squeeze on KBIO |url=https://moxreports.com/kbio-infinity-squeeze/ |access-date=2021-01-26 |website=Mox Reports |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122195010/https://moxreports.com/kbio-infinity-squeeze/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

發生於2021年1月的[[遊戲驛站軋空事件|遊戲驛站軋空事件]]現在仍在進行<ref>{{Cite web |last=Smith |first=Connor |title=Short Squeeze Sends GameStop Shares to 2007 Levels. What Happens Next. |url=https://www.barrons.com/articles/short-squeeze-sends-gamestop-shares-to-2007-levels-what-happens-next-51611348093 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124183939/https://www.barrons.com/articles/short-squeeze-sends-gamestop-shares-to-2007-levels-what-happens-next-51611348093 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |access-date=2021-01-25 |website=Barrons |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Ferré |first=Ines |title=GameStop shares soar 50% as massive short squeeze forges ahead |url=https://www.sports.yahoo.com/news/game-stop-shares-up-50-in-premarket-as-massive-short-squeeze-forges-ahead-133819632.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125152814/https://sports.yahoo.com/news/game-stop-shares-up-50-in-premarket-as-massive-short-squeeze-forges-ahead-133819632.html |archive-date=2021-01-25 |access-date=2021-01-25 |website=Yahoo! Sports |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該事件由[[Reddit|Reddit]]上的[[華爾街賭場|華爾街賭場]]討論版引發<ref name="yun li">{{Cite web |last=Li |first=Yun |date=January 27, 2021 |title=GameStop mania explained: How the Reddit retail trading crowd ran over Wall Street pros |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/27/gamestop-mania-explained-how-the-reddit-retail-trading-crowd-ran-over-wall-street-pros.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127221220/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/27/gamestop-mania-explained-how-the-reddit-retail-trading-crowd-ran-over-wall-street-pros.html |archive-date=2021-01-27 |access-date=2021-01-27 |website=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=D'Anastasio |first=Cecilia |title=A Fight Over GameStop's Soaring Stock Turns Ugly |url=https://www.wired.com/story/gamestop-stock-wall-street-bets-short-squeeze/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124173424/https://www.wired.com/story/gamestop-stock-wall-street-bets-short-squeeze/ |archive-date=2021-01-24 |access-date=2021-01-25 |website=Wired |language=en-us |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這次軋空令遊戲驛站股價在2021年1月28日創出483美元的歷史高位<ref name="NYSE">{{Cite web |title=NYSE GAMESTOP CORPORATION GME |url=https://www.nyse.com/quote/XNYS:GME |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119153914/https://www.nyse.com/quote/XNYS:GME |archive-date=2021-01-19 |access-date=2021-01-28 |website=www.nyse.com |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

